  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a 3D casual fast platform jump running game, you can get a unique and endless new exciting experience in the high-speed sprint and jump of cute small animals at sea.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Precise control platform jump in the cute cartoon world shuttle.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390870/extras/e981e88969bd8cd510234d1ac304714b.poster.avif?t=1741052517\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390870/extras/e981e88969bd8cd510234d1ac304714b.webm?t=1741052517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390870/extras/e981e88969bd8cd510234d1ac304714b.mp4?t=1741052517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With each more skilled control, you will bring more smooth and elegant experience</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390870/extras/125819254d4115185196a5421644b542.poster.avif?t=1741052517\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390870/extras/125819254d4115185196a5421644b542.webm?t=1741052517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390870/extras/125819254d4115185196a5421644b542.mp4?t=1741052517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ride your own wave board and enjoy every success in the thrill of extreme push.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390870/extras/d786b50ac7e65630977f7652edfb83a8.poster.avif?t=1741052517\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390870/extras/d786b50ac7e65630977f7652edfb83a8.webm?t=1741052517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390870/extras/d786b50ac7e65630977f7652edfb83a8.mp4?t=1741052517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world will applaud you when you complete the QTE rhythm jump.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Discord Community : </p>",
